Welcome to AFFORDABLE, FAST, EASY car rentals!

My name is Joresth, I’m a local professional real estate advisor helping people buy, sell, invest, and manage real estate, including new construction, in Utah. I also love cars and I love to share them!

To keep the cars in good running condition we ask you to take the time to read the listing description for the car you desire to rent. Although we are not perfect, perfection is what we strive for. Our cars are maintained regularly, if you have any feedback about the cars, we’d love to hear it! Please message us directly about anything we can do to provide better service.

We ask you to please be respectful of the cars, obey all traffic laws at all times, avoid driving directly behind semi trucks, trucks or big SUVs to avoid flying rocks from hitting the windshield and please read the listing description of the car you wish to rent before booking!

I also manage multiple short term rentals in Utah. If you or your party need a place to stay while in Utah feel free to send me a message and I'll try to get you a good deal.
Dedicated to provide you with the best car rental experience! We have cars located in Las Vegas, Salt Lake City, Bozeman and West Yellowstone.

I go by The Merovingian 😂 I hate driving 😳🤢🤮 and I don’t even like suv 🚙 but I notice they are very lucrative 😬. So I bought a bunch of lawnmowers 🥳…

All our rental rocket 🚀 get services once at month at the dealership! We want to make sure they are ready to conquer Pluto, the sun ☀️ and any galaxies 🌌 in between.
Some who's loves see people enjoy our before State and Driving a nice car!

Retired from the corporate world and joined Turo to add value to the many great people in and visiting beautiful Utah. As an active traveler over the past 20+ years, I understand the intricacies of travel.  In that regard, my goal is to make your trip with me as seamless and hassle free as possible.  I go out of my way to deliver amazing, showroom clean cars in excellent mechanical condition.  That way, you can focus on the journey ahead and not the wheels taking you there.

We're still a small operation with only 4-5 cars but that means every car gets a ton of attention when it comes to maintenance and cleaning.  

We are 100% AWD or 4WD plus we swap our wheels and tires out every season from all-season to 3PMSF winter-rated tires.

I've personally rented from a few of the larger Turo hosts and it's clear that attention to details get's left behind fairly quickly when fleet sizes get too big.

We're well over 250 trips with 100% 5-Star ratings and we'd like to deliver that same excellent experience to you and your families.  If there's we anything we can do to earn that one last star, please let us know!!

I am a healthcare professional serving the Salt Lake City community for over the past 22 years.  I'm an avid stock/options and cryptocurrency trader.  I love watching and playing sports.  I consider myself a huge sports fan!  I grew up in the mountains of SLC and you can find me skiing at Snowbird/Alta, fly fishing the Provo River, hiking the Wasatch mountains or catching some sun in beautiful St. George!  Im a father of 3 awesome children and I enjoy the side hustle Turo has provided.  Keep an eye on my Turo fleet, one of these days I would love to add a Dodge Charger Hellcat SRT Widebody!  Will be adding more cars soon. Stay tuned!!!
I find solutions for all personal transportation needs that increase convenience, and decrease the cost of getting around when you need a car.

With a diverse fleet of meticulously maintained vehicles ranging from compact cars to luxury SUVs, Sandoval's Rental caters to a wide array of transportation needs, whether it's for business, leisure, or special occasions. Our commitment to quality ensures that each vehicle is inspected and serviced regularly, guaranteeing safety and comfort for our valued customers.

What sets us apart is our unwavering dedication to customer satisfaction. Our friendly and knowledgeable staff are always on hand to assist with any inquiries and to provide personalized recommendations tailored to individual preferences. Whether it's a short-term rental or a long-term lease, we work tirelessly to accommodate the unique needs of every client.

At Sandoval's Rental, we understand that convenience is key. That's why we offer flexible booking options, competitive rates, and convenient pickup and drop-off locations to ensure a seamless rental experience from start to finish. Our goal is not just to provide transportation, but to create lasting memories and foster long-term relationships with our customers.

Experience the difference with Sandoval's Rental. Your journey begins with us.

bio.openEndedText:
After an amazing 25-year in corporate America I decided to retire to spend much more time with my amazing wife an two incredible daughters. Turo has been a ton of fun and we love providing top-notch cars for new friends like you.

We love to travel and lived for a decade in Paris, France and Vancouver, Canada and love everything European and Canadian! We'd still be living in Vancouver if I could have convinced my wife to stay lol!

We love visiting our family in PA (Go Steelers!), NC, and FL! We love Utah's amazing snow, mountains and national parks. Our daughters would say they're place to vacation is Los Cabos, MX and any other place where they can go swim with whale sharks!

You count on us for meticulously maintained vehicles, hot knife through butter-like snow tires and cars that are detailed after every use. No odors. We also tint all our vehicle windows to protect against Utah's powerful high-altitude UV rays and also add clear protective film in the front to stop rock chips and ensure our cars are always looking great!

In summer, we'll see you in the national parks and in winter we'll see you on the slopes!

Welcome to Altuve Grazziani.

We are a service-oriented company passionate about providing exceptional car rental experiences to our customers. We are here to make your journey comfortable, exciting, and memorable.

All our vehicles are maintained in optimal condition and undergo thorough cleaning before and after each rental. Our team is dedicated to providing you with exceptional service. 

We are here to answer your questions and assist you every step of the way. Book with us and discover the freedom to explore and the convenience of traveling in style. 

We look forward to serving you soon!

I was Born in San Francisco, California. Later raised in Hawaii and Southern Utah. I currently reside in Salt Lake City, Utah. I am a Husband, Father and a God Fearing Man. My Hobbies are really simple, I love to spend time with my Family, going to the Gym, watching Sports and Golfing. (Note: That does not mean I'm good at Golf)

     My Resume' is a combination of Sales, Finance and Entrepreneurship. I sold Cars, did Auto Finance, Consumer Lending and Indirect Lending for a total of 9 years, which finally would lead me to doing Mortgages for almost 4 years. I did these things working for Multi Million and Billion Dollar Companies. During those Years I built a Portfolio of Personal Investment properties and created a Real Estate Rental Management company that I am blessed to call my own. 

     Given my History, when I first learned about Turo and began my months of research, it honestly was nothing new to me. I am passionate about helping and serving others. This is what drove me to become a Full Time Host. Let me know how I can help you.
